00:35:23,279 --> 00:35:24,120
I mentioned this morning

766
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:25,400
that I was reading through the book of Nehemiah.

767
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:28,500
I've been reading some other prophets recently.

768
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,540
You know, it's kind of interesting

769
00:35:30,540 --> 00:35:34,360
when you see what the nation of Israel suffered

770
00:35:35,040 --> 00:35:36,720
and how they responded.

771
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:38,660
Not all of them, but some of them.

772
00:35:40,620 --> 00:35:43,080
And here the psalmist says, before I was afflicted,

773
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:47,080
I went astray, but now, so after the affliction,

774
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,580
have I kept thy word.

775
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:51,840
I would hope tonight that we would not have

776
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:56,080
to suffer affliction or suffer some great hardship

777
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:57,620
in order to seek the Lord.

778
00:36:00,080 --> 00:36:03,200
But that we would truly just say, I wanna seek God.

779
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:08,160
I don't wanna wander from thy commandments.

780
00:36:08,160 --> 00:36:11,720
No, I wanna walk with the Lord.

781
00:36:11,720 --> 00:36:15,680
I wanna continue until the day of my departure,

782
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:17,400
whenever that is.

783
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:20,360
And so here's some thoughts from the psalmist.

784
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:22,760
Again, four actions, three resolutions,

785
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:26,160
that maybe tonight, as we examine our lives this week,

786
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:28,220
as we go through our lives and we say,

787
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:29,960
you know, these are some things

788
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:32,760
that I need to incorporate in my life.

789
00:36:33,279 --> 00:36:36,320
I know if I'm seeking God with my whole heart or not.

790
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:39,440
I know if I'm hiding God's word in my heart or not.

791
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:42,840
I can go back and I can look at my life and say,

792
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:45,640
when was the last time I memorized a verse of scripture?

793
00:36:47,559 --> 00:36:49,300
I said this to someone recently.

794
00:36:49,300 --> 00:36:52,400
I can go in my life and I can look back and say,

795
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:55,200
when was the last time I shared the gospel with someone?

796
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:59,640
Not the last time someone, I was able to lead them to Christ

797
00:36:59,640 --> 00:37:02,420
because that's God's business.

798
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:03,940
But our business is to give the gospel.

799
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:05,140
When was the last time I tried

800
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:07,200
to even share the gospel with someone?

801
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,140
I even cared enough to talk to them about their soul.

802
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:13,940
When's the last time I hid a Bible verse in my heart?

803
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:16,580
And as we evaluate our lives, as we begin to,

804
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:17,980
it is always this time of year,

805
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,660
you go into a new year and all those things,

806
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:21,380
good time for evaluation.

807
00:37:22,380 --> 00:37:24,340
The psalmist says, I don't wanna wander.

808
00:37:24,340 --> 00:37:27,340
I hope tonight we'd say, I don't wanna wander.

809
00:37:27,340 --> 00:37:29,700
I wanna keep on keeping on,

810
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:32,100
keep serving God, living for God.

811
00:37:32,779 --> 00:37:34,380
Let's take these actions and these resolutions

812
00:37:34,380 --> 00:37:36,940
and apply them in our lives, shall we pray?

813
00:37:36,940 --> 00:37:38,820
Father, we love you tonight.

814
00:37:38,820 --> 00:37:40,100
We thank you for loving us.

815
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:41,500
We thank you for your word

816
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:43,580
and for the truth contained therein.

817
00:37:43,580 --> 00:37:45,220
I pray God that you would help us

818
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:48,500
to be able to be students of your word

819
00:37:48,500 --> 00:37:51,700
and Lord, to seek you with our whole heart,

820
00:37:51,700 --> 00:37:55,620
to seek your word, Lord, to search the scriptures daily.

821
00:37:57,460 --> 00:38:01,420
Lord, that we would hide your word in our hearts.

822
00:38:01,779 --> 00:38:04,660
Lord, that we would be doers of the word,

823
00:38:04,660 --> 00:38:07,940
that we would speak and declare thy word.

824
00:38:07,940 --> 00:38:09,059
Help us, Lord.

825
00:38:10,779 --> 00:38:12,300
I pray that you'd move and work

826
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:15,100
in this time of invitation as only you can.

827
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:16,900
And we'll be careful to give you the honor and glory

828
00:38:16,900 --> 00:38:19,340
for every decision made, for it's in Christ's name we pray.

829
00:38:19,340 --> 00:38:20,540
Would you stand with me?

